---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="About - AI-Assisted Development"
  description="Learn about my approach to rapid prototyping and AI-assisted development, and how I leverage AI tools to build projects quickly."
>
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1 class="hero-title">About AI-Assisted Development</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        Exploring the future of rapid prototyping through AI collaboration
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-intro">
    <div class="intro-grid">
      <div class="intro-text">
        <h2>Hello, I'm a Developer</h2>
        <p>
          I'm passionate about exploring the intersection of human creativity and artificial intelligence 
          in software development. This showcase represents my journey in rapid prototyping, where I've 
          built functional applications in 2-4 hours each, with approximately 90% of the code generated 
          using AI tools.
        </p>
        <p>
          My background includes full-stack development, with experience in modern frameworks and a 
          deep interest in how AI can accelerate the development process while maintaining code quality 
          and best practices.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="intro-visual">
        <div class="skill-bubbles">
          <div class="skill-bubble">üöÄ Rapid Prototyping</div>
          <div class="skill-bubble">ü§ñ AI Integration</div>
          <div class="skill-bubble">‚ö° Quick Iteration</div>
          <div class="skill-bubble">üí° Creative Problem Solving</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="ai-approach">
    <h2 class="section-title">My AI-Assisted Development Approach</h2>
    
    <div class="approach-grid">
      <div class="approach-card">
        <div class="approach-icon">üéØ</div>
        <h3>Strategic Planning</h3>
        <p>
          I start each project by clearly defining the problem and scope. AI helps me brainstorm 
          solutions, architecture decisions, and identify the most efficient development path.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="approach-card">
        <div class="approach-icon">‚ö°</div>
        <h3>Rapid Code Generation</h3>
        <p>
          Using AI tools like GitHub Copilot, ChatGPT, and Claude, I generate boilerplate code, 
          implement complex logic, and create comprehensive test suites in minutes rather than hours.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="approach-card">
        <div class="approach-icon">üîç</div>
        <h3>Quality Assurance</h3>
        <p>
          While AI generates most of the code, I focus on reviewing, refining, and ensuring the 
          output meets best practices, security standards, and performance requirements.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="approach-card">
        <div class="approach-icon">üé®</div>
        <h3>Creative Direction</h3>
        <p>
          I provide the creative vision, user experience considerations, and design decisions. 
          AI handles the implementation while I guide the overall direction and functionality.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="tools-section">
    <h2 class="section-title">AI Tools & Technologies</h2>
    
    <div class="tools-grid">
      <div class="tool-category">
        <h3>AI Development Tools</h3>
        <ul class="tool-list">
          <li>GitHub Copilot - Code completion and generation</li>
          <li>ChatGPT - Architecture planning and problem solving</li>
          <li>Claude - Code review and optimization</li>
          <li>Cursor IDE - AI-powered development environment</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="tool-category">
        <h3>Development Stack</h3>
        <ul class="tool-list">
          <li>Frontend: React, Vue.js, Svelte, Astro</li>
          <li>Backend: Node.js, Python, Express, FastAPI</li>
          <li>Database: MongoDB, PostgreSQL, Firebase</li>
          <li>Deployment: Vercel, Netlify, Docker</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="tool-category">
        <h3>Design & UI</h3>
        <ul class="tool-list">
          <li>Tailwind CSS - Rapid styling</li>
          <li>Figma - Design and prototyping</li>
          <li>Lucide Icons - Beautiful iconography</li>
          <li>AI-generated assets and graphics</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="philosophy">
    <div class="philosophy-content">
      <h2>Development Philosophy</h2>
      <div class="philosophy-grid">
        <div class="philosophy-item">
          <h3>Human-AI Collaboration</h3>
          <p>
            I believe the future of development lies not in replacing human creativity, but in 
            amplifying it. AI handles repetitive tasks while I focus on innovation, user experience, 
            and creative problem-solving.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="philosophy-item">
          <h3>Rapid Iteration</h3>
          <p>
            By leveraging AI for code generation, I can iterate quickly on ideas, test concepts, 
            and bring prototypes to life in hours rather than days or weeks.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="philosophy-item">
          <h3>Learning & Adaptation</h3>
          <p>
            Each project is a learning opportunity. I continuously refine my AI prompting skills, 
            discover new tools, and adapt my workflow to maximize efficiency and quality.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="philosophy-item">
          <h3>Open Source Mindset</h3>
          <p>
            All projects are open source, demonstrating transparency in AI-assisted development 
            and contributing to the community's understanding of these emerging workflows.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="stats-detailed">
    <h2 class="section-title">Development Metrics</h2>
    
    <div class="stats-grid">
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-icon">‚è±Ô∏è</div>
        <div class="stat-number">2-4</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Hours per Project</div>
        <div class="stat-description">
          From concept to deployment, including planning, development, and testing
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-icon">ü§ñ</div>
        <div class="stat-number">~90%</div>
        <div class="stat-label">AI-Generated Code</div>
        <div class="stat-description">
          Percentage of code generated using AI tools, with human oversight and refinement
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-icon">üöÄ</div>
        <div class="stat-number">15+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Projects Completed</div>
        <div class="stat-description">
          Functional applications built using AI-assisted development methodologies
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-icon">üìà</div>
        <div class="stat-number">10x</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Speed Improvement</div>
        <div class="stat-description">
          Estimated development speed increase compared to traditional coding methods
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="cta-content">
      <h2>Let's Connect</h2>
      <p>
        Interested in AI-assisted development or have questions about my approach? 
        I'd love to discuss techniques, share insights, or explore collaboration opportunities.
      </p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get in Touch</a>
        <a href="/projects" class="btn btn-secondary">View Projects</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* About Hero */
  .about-hero {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffd89b 0%, #19547b 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* About Intro */
  .about-intro {
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .intro-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .intro-text h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .intro-text p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .intro-visual {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .skill-bubbles {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    max-width: 400px;
  }

  .skill-bubble {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-align: center;
    color: white;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .skill-bubble:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  }

  /* AI Approach Section */
  .ai-approach {
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .approach-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .approach-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .approach-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }

  .approach-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .approach-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .approach-card p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Tools Section */
  .tools-section {
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .tools-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .tool-category {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .tool-category h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .tool-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .tool-list li {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .tool-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  /* Philosophy Section */
  .philosophy {
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .philosophy-content h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .philosophy-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .philosophy-item {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border-left: 4px solid;
    border-image: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%) 1;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
  }

  .philosophy-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .philosophy-item p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Detailed Stats */
  .stats-detailed {
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .stat-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .stat-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }

  .stat-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .stat-description {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* CTA Section */
  .cta-section {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-content p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
    color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.5);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    color: white;
    border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  }

  /* Responsive Design */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-title {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .intro-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .skill-bubbles {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      max-width: 300px;
    }

    .approach-grid,
    .tools-grid,
    .philosophy-grid,
    .stats-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .btn {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 300px;
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>